In the search bar on Telegram, type "BotFather" and send the command "/newbot".

The BotFather will ask for a name for your bot, after it will ask for a username as well.

Copy the generated access Token.

Send any message to your bot by Telegram.

Go to the settings tab, paste your token and push the "Get ID" button to get your ID and save.


Tips:

You can manually add your ID, access the following address changing (TOKENHERE) by the copied token.

https://api.telegram.org/bot(TOKENHERE)/getUpdates

The same tutorial is available on the Github page with images.

http://github.com/warflop/Telebix
